::Perndabot/Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Perndabot apears back in the cave, blinking. He exits the cave, his 
scanners trying to pick up the energy signature he had been chasing.

After a few steps, they beep. He looks down at them and grins. There 
was another Maximal with the first one! Oh well, just one more to 
kill then.

The huge bot once again activates his jetpack, flying off toward 
Shadow Wing and Lunarpine.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Reptilica and Bloodystrike apear back at the Alliance base. Feeling 
the ship shake, they run off down a hallway, heading for the exit to 
check it out.
